JEN, I'M NOT A BAD GUY.
I JUST WANT TO HAVE FUN.

29:13.375 --> 29:15.000
WELL, THEN TELL ME,

29:15.000 --> 29:20.750
CHRISTOPHER ROBBIN,
WHAT IS YOUR IDEA OF FUN?

29:21.166 --> 29:22.667
THIS.

29:31.417 --> 29:34.959
SO, JEN...
ARE WE ON THE SAME PAGE?

29:36.417 --> 29:37.875
SAME PAGE.

30:00.667 --> 30:04.917
IS SHE OK?
YEAH. SHE'LL BE FINE.

30:04.917 --> 30:07.417
SHE JUST WANTS TO BE ALONE
RIGHT NOW, YOU KNOW?

30:08.208 --> 30:10.208
WHY DIDN'T YOU JUST WRITE "NO"?

30:13.208 --> 30:14.834
I DIDN'T WANT TO LIE TO HER.

30:16.583 --> 30:18.667
I MEAN, I DON'T KNOW.
WHAT WOULD YOU HAVE DONE?

30:20.166 --> 30:22.166
I'D LIKE TO THINK I WOULD
HAVE BEEN HONEST.

30:24.125 --> 30:25.375
I DON'T KNOW. IT'S...

30:25.375 --> 30:28.333
...I SEEM TO HAVE TROUBLE SAYING
A LOT OF THINGS LATELY.

30:31.083 --> 30:34.875
YOU KNOW WHAT?
WHAT?

30:36.083 --> 30:37.667
TRY HARDER.

30:51.083 --> 30:55.041
LOOK, NO MORE ROUNDS TONIGHT,
DAWSON. I AM SO TIRED.

30:55.041 --> 30:57.083
I'M ACTUALLY TRYING TO GET
5 MINUTES OF STUDYING IN.

31:00.333 --> 31:02.250
JO, I THOUGHT WHAT WE HAD
WAS SPECIAL.

31:02.250 --> 31:06.750
LOOK, I'M SERIOUS. I DON'T WANT
TO TALK ABOUT ANYTHING BUT THIS.

31:06.750 --> 31:08.792
YOU WROTE THAT YOU HAVE
BEEN IN LOVE TWICE.

31:11.333 --> 31:12.792
YOU LOOKED AT MY TEST?!

31:12.792 --> 31:14.291
NO, I'VE LEARNED MY LESSON ABOUT
INVADING YOUR PRIVACY.

31:14.291 --> 31:17.875
CHRIS'S SISTER WAS KIND ENOUGH
TO IMPART THAT INFORMATION.

31:17.875 --> 31:19.959
JOEY, YOU SAID THAT
I WAS YOUR WORLD.

31:19.959 --> 31:22.208
WHEN DID YOU HAVE TIME
FOR GUY #2?

31:22.208 --> 31:23.208
I DON'T BELIEVE YOU'RE
SHALLOW ENOUGH

31:23.208 --> 31:25.667
TO FALL IN LOVE WITH JACK
AFTER ONE KISS.

31:25.667 --> 31:27.166
LOOK, STOP IT!
I DON'T UNDERSTAND!

31:27.166 --> 31:28.542
LOOK, I DON'T KNOW, OK?!

31:28.542 --> 31:30.375
WHY CAN'T WE GO BACK
TO THE WAY THINGS WERE?

31:30.375 --> 31:31.917
WHY CAN'T WE
JUST BE FRIENDS, DAWSON?

31:31.917 --> 31:33.458
THAT'S REALLY WHAT YOU WANT?
YES!

31:33.458 --> 31:34.542
AFTER ALL WE'VE BEEN
THROUGH, JUST FRIENDS?

31:34.542 --> 31:36.834
YEAH.

31:36.834 --> 31:38.041
IF YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND
WHY THAT CAN'T HAPPEN,

31:38.041 --> 31:42.041
IF YOU DON'T GET THAT,
YOU DON'T GET ME!

31:51.708 --> 31:56.041
VERY EMOTIONAL.
OSCAR NOMINATING. REALLY.

31:56.583 --> 31:58.792
GO AWAY.

32:00.083 --> 32:02.959
DAWSON, YOU AREN'T CRYING,
ARE YOU?

32:02.959 --> 32:05.750
YOU WANTED A KISS.
IS THAT WHAT YOU WANT?

32:05.750 --> 32:08.208
ARE YOU PREPARED FOR EVERYTHING
THAT COMES WITH THAT KISS?

32:08.208 --> 32:10.250
'CAUSE IT DOESN'T JUST END
WITH A FADE OUT.

32:10.250 --> 32:12.458
THERE ARE REPERCUSSIONS.
HEARTS GET BROKEN.

32:12.458 --> 32:13.708
FRIENDSHIPS GET RUINED.

32:13.708 --> 32:15.959
YOUR ENTIRE LIFE COULD
FALL APART BECAUSE OF ONE KISS.

32:15.959 --> 32:17.834
THAT'S WHAT YOU HAVE TO LOOK
FORWARD TO.

32:17.834 --> 32:20.417
DO YOURSELF A BIG FAVOR...
DON'T RUSH IT.

33:06.542 --> 33:07.125
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

33:07.125 --> 33:08.834
Joey: KNOCK, KNOCK.

33:08.834 --> 33:10.083
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

33:12.375 --> 33:15.208
TO HANG OUT WITH THE ONLY SANE
INDIVIDUAL HERE.

33:17.792 --> 33:19.083
HE'S SO MEAN.

33:22.083 --> 33:23.458
ALL BOYS ARE.

33:23.458 --> 33:26.834
IT'S THEIR EASIEST WAY
OF EXPRESSING THEMSELVES.

33:26.834 --> 33:31.083
AFTER TONIGHT, I'M AVOIDING
GROWING UP AT ALL COSTS.

33:31.083 --> 33:33.125
SOUNDS GOOD. LET ME KNOW
IF YOU HAVE ANY LUCK.

33:36.000 --> 33:39.250
AREN'T YOU SUPPOSED TO BE
ARGUING THE OTHER SIDE?

33:39.250 --> 33:41.959
CONVINCING ME THAT
GROWING UP CAN BE

33:41.959 --> 33:44.667
SUCH A BEAUTIFUL EXPERIENCE
IF I JUST LET IT?

33:44.667 --> 33:46.458
I SEE.

33:46.458 --> 33:49.458
YOU WANT THE "I'M OLDER THAN
YOU, SO HERE'S HOW IT WORKS"
SPEECH?

33:50.667 --> 33:53.834
HOW'S THIS?
GROWING UP SUCKS.

33:53.834 --> 33:55.375
NOT ALL KISSES ARE MAGIC,

33:55.375 --> 33:58.875
AND MOST BOYS DO NOT LIVE UP
TO YOUR EXPECTATIONS,

34:01.458 --> 34:08.083
BUT THERE ARE THOSE TIMES WHEN
EVERYTHING, I MEAN LOVE,

34:08.083 --> 34:10.458
ROMANCE, RELATIONSHIPS,

34:10.458 --> 34:15.166
IT ALL FALLS TOGETHER PERFECTLY
AND IT'S INCREDIBLE.

34:17.041 --> 34:21.542
IT'S THOSE MOMENTS, NO MATTER
HOW DEPRESSINGLY FEW AND FAR
BETWEEN,

34:21.542 --> 34:22.208
THAT MAKE GROWING UP WORTH IT.

34:24.625 --> 34:27.041
YOU'LL BE OK.

35:19.750 --> 35:23.542
[CLOCK BELL TOLLS]

35:26.333 --> 35:29.041
OH, MY GOD!
TELL ME IT IS NOT 6 AM.

35:29.041 --> 35:30.500
IT'S 6AM.

35:30.500 --> 35:32.041
WAKE UP, WAKE UP!

35:32.041 --> 35:36.500
PACEY, THE TEST IS IN 4 HOURS.

35:36.500 --> 35:39.000
OH MY GOD! I MUST HAVE BEEN
STUDYING AND I PASSED OUT.

35:39.000 --> 35:41.458
HEY, RELAX. WHERE'S THE BINDER?

35:41.458 --> 35:42.875
BINDER'S ON THE PORCH,
I'LL GET IT.

35:42.875 --> 35:43.959
WE DON'T HAVE ANY TIME!

35:43.959 --> 35:45.959
WHAT'S HAPPENING?
WHERE IS EVERYONE?

35:45.959 --> 35:48.458
EVERYONE IS TOTALLY ASLEEP,
TOTALLY UNSTUDIED,

35:48.458 --> 35:51.250
TOTALLY UNPREPARED,
AND TOTALLY SCREWED!

35:57.667 --> 36:00.792
MORNING.

36:00.792 --> 36:03.458
HEY.

36:03.458 --> 36:07.041
THEY'RE GETTING UP.
WE SHOULD GET DOWN THERE.

36:15.834 --> 36:18.208
THANK YOU.

36:19.834 --> 36:22.166
FOR?

36:22.166 --> 36:23.792
FOR A VERY FUN NIGHT.

36:25.041 --> 36:27.834
HANG ON A SEC, I'LL GET
DRESSED AND COME DOWN WITH YOU.

36:27.834 --> 36:30.375
NO, NO. THAT'S COOL.
JUST, TAKE YOUR TIME.

36:31.458 --> 36:32.917
I'LL MEET YOU
DOWN THERE.

36:38.083 --> 36:39.500
ALRIGHT, EVERYBODY, LISTEN UP!

36:39.500 --> 36:42.375
WE GOT EXACTLY FOUR
CONCENTRATED HOURS

36:42.375 --> 36:45.792
IN WHICH TO STUDY FOR THE
DEADLIEST EXAM OF OUR YOUNG
ADULT LIVES.

36:45.792 --> 36:50.125
NOW, GOING OFF AN ABBREVIATED
VERSION OF ANDIE'S LESSON PLAN,

36:50.125 --> 36:54.041
I PLAN ON CONSTRUCTING A 3 HOUR
AND 45 MINUTE LESSON PLAN,

36:54.041 --> 36:57.500
WHICH, IF EXECUTED PROPERLY,
WILL COVER EVERYTHING.

36:57.500 --> 36:58.875
YOU FOLLOWING ME?

36:58.875 --> 37:03.041
PACEY, THIS TEST IS WAY TOO...
SHH! LISTEN, DON'T WORRY.

37:03.041 --> 37:07.375
BOYS AND GIRLS, YOU HAPPEN TO BE
IN THE HANDS OF A PROFESSIONAL
CRAMMER.

37:07.375 --> 37:08.750
LET'S START WITH BEOWULF.

37:08.750 --> 37:10.875
HOW MANY MONSTERS DID HE
HAVE TO FIGHT AND NAME ONE.

37:10.875 --> 37:12.583
THREE.
GRENDEL.

37:12.583 --> 37:16.041
GOOD, NOW ON TO THE HARD STUFF.

37:16.041 --> 37:18.542
WHICH ONE OF THE BRONTE
SISTERS WROTE WUTHERING HEIGHTS?

37:18.542 --> 37:19.333
EMILY.
CHARLOTTE.

37:19.333 --> 37:21.792
IT WAS EMILY.
CHARLOTTE!

37:21.792 --> 37:23.000
CHARLOTTE WROTE JANE EYRE.

37:23.000 --> 37:25.041
THEN WHAT DID EMILY WRITE?
WUTHERING HEIGHTS.

37:25.041 --> 37:27.375
"TO BE OR NOT TO BE.
THAT IS THE QUESTION."

37:27.375 --> 37:29.875
"WHETHER IT IS NOBLER IN THE
MIND TO SUFFER THE SLINGS..."

37:29.875 --> 37:31.834
NAME THE LITTLE PEOPLE IN
GULLIVER'S TRAVELS.

37:31.834 --> 37:33.250
LILLIPUTIANS.

37:33.250 --> 37:35.625
THE BIG BAD SCARY PEOPLE.
BROB...

37:35.625 --> 37:39.583
BROB... BROB...
BROMD... BROM..

37:39.583 --> 37:41.291
D-DING?

37:41.291 --> 37:43.583
"ARMS AGAINST A SEA
OF TROUBLES."

37:43.583 --> 37:45.542
TO SLEEP..

37:45.542 --> 37:48.500
NAME THREE OCCUPATIONS OF
TRAVELERS IN THE CANTERBURY
TALES.

37:48.500 --> 37:50.250
KNIGHT!
SUMMONER!

37:50.250 --> 37:53.125
COME ON! COME ON!
DID WE SAY KNIGHT?

37:53.125 --> 37:57.041
"AND BY A SLEEP TO SAY WE END."

37:57.041 --> 38:00.333
"TO DIE, TO SLEEP, TO
SLEEP PERCHANCE TO DREAM."

38:00.333 --> 38:01.375
I'LL BUY IT.

38:01.375 --> 38:03.500
BROMDAMING!
BROMDAMING!

38:03.500 --> 38:05.667
BROBDINGNAGIANS.

38:05.667 --> 38:08.667
CONGRATULATIONS, GUYS,
WE'RE DONE,

38:08.667 --> 38:10.750
BUT I GOT ONE LAST
GROUP ACTIVITY.

38:43.917 --> 38:45.583
HEY.

38:45.583 --> 38:48.333
WOW. YOU REALLY TOOK
CONTROL IN THERE.

38:48.333 --> 38:50.333
YOU HAVE AN INTERESTING WAY
OF DOING THAT.

38:50.333 --> 38:52.417
YEAH, WELL, I PERFORM WELL
UNDER PRESSURE.

38:52.417 --> 38:54.291
I WANT TO EXPLAIN
SOMETHING TO YOU.

38:54.291 --> 38:56.333
YOU REALLY DON'T HAVE
TO TALK ABOUT THIS, ANDIE.

38:56.333 --> 38:57.667
I DO, PACEY.

38:57.667 --> 39:00.917
I MEAN, I'M THE QUEEN OF
KEEPING DIRTY SECRETS.

39:00.917 --> 39:05.250
SO I UNDERSTAND WHY YOU DIDN'T
JUMP FORWARD WITH THE
INFORMATION.

39:05.250 --> 39:07.750
I THINK I WAS JUST MORE
SHOCKED BY THE IDEA

39:07.750 --> 39:14.125
THAT YOU HAVE SO MUCH
EXPERIENCE AND I, UM...

39:14.125 --> 39:17.166
WILL.

39:17.166 --> 39:19.667
YOU'RE SUCH A JERK!
A SLACKER JERK.

39:19.667 --> 39:25.875
A CHAMPION SLACKER JERK.
AND WHAT DOES THAT MAKE YOU?

39:25.875 --> 39:28.041
I DON'T KNOW, PACEY.
YOU TELL ME.

39:28.041 --> 39:29.500
I DARE YOU.

39:30.834 --> 39:36.333
YOU, ANDIE McPHEE, ARE THE GIRL
THAT I LOVE TO HATE.

39:36.333 --> 39:38.542
I LOVE TO HATE YOU, TOO.

39:47.875 --> 39:49.583
[SIGHS]

39:49.583 --> 39:50.792
NOT FORGIVEN.
IT'S A NO?

39:55.208 --> 39:55.542
HEY.

39:57.333 --> 40:01.667
HEY.
CAN WE TALK?

40:06.083 --> 40:08.333
SURE.

40:11.375 --> 40:13.291
DO ME A FAVOR AND DON'T SAY
ANYTHING, OK?

40:13.291 --> 40:15.291
EVERY TIME WE SPEAK,
I ALWAYS SCREW THIS UP.

40:15.291 --> 40:17.583
JUST PLEASE LISTEN.

40:18.083 --> 40:21.417
OK?

40:21.417 --> 40:24.875
ALL I'VE BEEN THINKING ABOUT
LATELY IS HOW MUCH I WANT TO
TAKE BACK OUR FIRST KISS.

40:24.875 --> 40:28.750
HOW MUCH I WOULD PAY TO JUST LET
YOU CLIMB THROUGH THAT WINDOW.

40:28.750 --> 40:32.417
I MEAN, WHO KNOWS WHAT
WOULD HAVE HAPPENED?

40:32.417 --> 40:34.083
MAYBE WE'D STILL
BE BEST FRIENDS.

40:34.083 --> 40:35.875
MAYBE YOU'D EVEN STILL
HAVE A THING FOR ME.

40:35.875 --> 40:39.875
I JUST KNOW THAT I
WOULDN'T BE HURTING LIKE THIS.

40:43.125 --> 40:45.000
BUT THEN I THINK ABOUT...

40:46.083 --> 40:48.917
...EVERYTHING THAT KISS
BROUGHT INTO MY LIFE.

40:48.917 --> 40:52.792
WHAT IT WAS LIKE TO LOOK AT YOU
AND KNOW NOT JUST WHAT YOU WERE
THINKING,

40:52.792 --> 40:56.333
BUT ALSO WHAT YOU WERE FEELING
BECAUSE I WAS FEELING THE SAME
THING,

40:58.417 --> 41:00.250
AND THEN IT'S WORTH IT.

41:02.458 --> 41:04.500
IT'S WORTH ALL THE PAIN
THAT I'M GOING THROUGH.

41:04.500 --> 41:08.375
I WANT TO REGRET KISSING YOU,
JOEY, BUT I CAN'T.

41:09.375 --> 41:12.291
IT WAS THE SMARTEST DECISION
I EVER MADE.

41:14.959 --> 41:19.291
DAWSON, THE TWO TIMES I
FELL IN LOVE,

41:19.291 --> 41:23.708
ON THE TEST,
THEY WERE BOTH YOU.

41:25.959 --> 41:29.959
I MEAN, THE FIRST TIME
I FELL WAS FOR MY FRIEND,

41:29.959 --> 41:32.458
THE DAWSON I GREW UP WITH,
THE BOY ACROSS THE CREEK,

41:32.458 --> 41:35.625
AND THE SECOND TIME
WAS AFTER WE KISSED.

41:35.625 --> 41:38.959
I MEAN, YOU BECAME THIS
WHOLE NEW PERSON TO ME AND...

41:38.959 --> 41:42.250
I FELL IN LOVE ALL OVER AGAIN.

41:42.250 --> 41:44.750
I MEAN, JUST BECAUSE
WE'RE NOT TOGETHER ANYMORE

41:44.750 --> 41:46.750
DOES NOT CHANGE
MY FEELINGS FOR YOU, DAWSON.

41:46.750 --> 41:49.750
IT'S ME I'M UNSURE OF.

41:52.834 --> 41:54.834
JOEY, I'M GOING TO GIVE
YOU THAT SPACE.

41:56.333 --> 42:02.333
NO HOSTILITY, NO UNDERHANDED
COMMENTS, JUST SPACE.

42:02.333 --> 42:04.917
BUT THAT DOESN'T CHANGE THE
WAY I FEEL ABOUT YOU.

42:07.208 --> 42:07.834
NOTHING CAN CHANGE THAT.

42:48.208 --> 42:48.834
COME ON, DAWSON!
LET'S GO!

43:07.375 --> 43:11.417
"DEAR CLASS, SOMETIMES
PREPARATION TEACHES YOU MORE
THAN THE EXAM ITSELF THEREFORE,

43:11.417 --> 43:13.834
YOU HAVE MORE OF IT.

43:13.834 --> 43:16.417
MY ILLNESS HAS CLAIMED ME FOR
ANOTHER DAY. TEST RESCHEDULED."

43:16.417 --> 43:17.834
[ALL SIGH]

43:17.834 --> 43:21.500
WELL, LOOKS LIKE WE CRAMMED
ALL NIGHT FOR NOTHING.

43:21.500 --> 43:23.500
NOW WHAT ARE WE SUPPOSED TO DO?

43:23.500 --> 43:25.291
GO TO OUR OTHER CLASSES,
I GUESS.

43:25.291 --> 43:28.417
ACTUALLY, NO.
I GOT ONE LAST GROUP ACTIVITY.

43:28.417 --> 43:29.917
FOLLOW ME.
